title: Number of live births in the EU in 2018
yAxis: Number of live births in millions
summary: Overall Number of live births in millions has decreased over the Year.

Number of live births in millions is slightly decreasing from 2010 to 2011, roughly constant from 2011 to 2012, slightly decreasing from 2012 to 2013, roughly constant from 2013 to 2016, and finally slightly decreasing from 2016 to 2017.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
Maximum Number of live births in millions, about 5.41 was reported at Year 2010
Minimum Number of live births in millions about 5.07 was reached at Year 2017
